    metaTitle: "Rehab Progression Protocols — PTA Clinical Decision Guide | NurseNest Allied",
    metaDescription: "PTA guide to rehabilitation progression protocols covering phase-based rehab, progression criteria, clinical milestones, and evidence-based guidelines for NPTE-PTA exam prep.",
    targetKeyword: "rehabilitation progression protocols PTA",
